data.description: **FULLY ASSUMABLE LOAN w/ 5.375% RATE!! ** This inviting 3-bedroom home, featuring a den and a family room, is perfectly situated to capture an abundance of natural light thanks to its North/South exposure. Located in Maricopa's most desirable neighborhood, Rancho El Dorado, this lake subdivision is exceptional. The home also boasts granite countertops, kitchen island, breakfast bar, eat-in kitchen area, and a breakfast room offering a charming spot for your morning coffee or casual meals. The amenities don't stop at your doorstep. The community offers a refreshing pool, a serene lake, and kids' playground. This home's design, modern amenities, and access to recreational facilities make it a standout in the market. Don't miss out on this fantastic home!
